org.forgerock.i18n.jul

Class LocalizedLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.i18n.jul.LocalizedLogger

  • public final class LocalizedLogger
extends Object
    A logger implementation which formats and localizes messages before forwarding them to an underlying Java Logger. For performance reasons this implementation will only localize and format messages if logging has been enabled for the associated log level and marker (if present).
